# =============================================================================
# DECRYPTED MEDIA / BIOMETRIC WORKING DIRS — NEVER COMMIT
# =============================================================================
# Gallery import/classification jobs decrypt media to local disk transiently
# (face/CLIP matching needs plaintext images). These dirs hold decrypted
# originals, face/CLIP embedding banks (biometric data), who-is-who mappings,
# and copied OAuth secrets. They are wiped after a job, but guard against ever
# committing them. Matches the ~/hidden-gallery-import working-dir convention
# and any *-gallery-import / *-photo-export scratch dir created in-repo.
*-gallery-import/
*-photo-export/
gallery-import/
photo-export/
hidden-gallery-import/
# biometric embedding banks + classification artifacts
*ref_face_bank*.npz
*clip_bank*.npz
*ref_embeddings*.npz
classification.json
upload_plan.json
new_clusters.json
uploaded_ledger.json
# copied collector/OAuth secrets staged locally for a job
collector.env.local
*.env.local
